{"tid":758814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】支那賤畜聲稱偷咗黃子華隻杯    放售599人仔 歡迎面交","createTime":"2018-07-28T05:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T05:13:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f18567d30db3576fbec8e675367d11265c330c9f","tid":758814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180728/58496338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58496338&d=uBYLp38IdER8mI%2BiaMykef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4d705cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58496338&h=01830b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180728/58496338</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180728/large/1532753982_af34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180728%2Flarge%2F1532753982_af34.jpg&h=8bc17b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180728/large/1532753981_85d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180728%2Flarge%2F1532753981_85d7.jpg&h=ff67e20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》A1頭條詳細揭露呢30名大陸變種黃牛黨如何「兩手空空」來港，壓價收購本土黃牛黨嘅黃子華門票，再以高價轉售俾大陸同胞。劏客又劏黃牛。鮮血淋漓，估計埋單可勁賺逾80萬港元。主腦「鳥叔」豪言，劏牛所賺，足夠喺家鄉湖南買樓。（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LKC2ZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LKC2ZE&d=uBYLp38IdER8mI%2BiaMykef755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e74b4448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LKC2ZE</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n要賺錢買樓，除咗妙手空空，有啲就比較有誠意嘅。如以下要介紹嘅奇人。<br />\n<br />\n呢位奇人用簡體字喺網上放售一隻杯。呢隻杯，唔係普通杯，而係黃子華o浪過口用嘅「回水o浪口杯」。呢位網民聲稱子華係用嚟飲過水。佢仲好驚好驚你哋唔信，話明係「親自在場館偷回來的」。<br />\n<br />\n至於呢隻子華神杯交易方法，包括：自提，當面交易，郵寄。<br />\n<br />\n唔記得講幾錢，係599蚊人仔，寫明不講價。<br />\n<br />\n即係咁，隻杯成本幾錢，大家心中有數啦，咁子華神就賣每隻$100；而呢位自稱偷咗隻杯嘅賊，以身犯險（估計係啦）、隻杯仲有子華神嘅DNA（神嘅DNA喎！）咁都只係賣599蚊人仔！！！！賣得咁平，會唔會侮辱咗子華神？<br />\n<br />\n如果黃子華約佢面交，唔知會點？<br />\n<br />\n賣賊贓（物主聲稱係）仲要唔俾講價，而且可以「面交」咁大膽，都話咗玻璃強國人民真係勁。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提。都係關隻杯事。今日凌晨一點左右，黃子華官方fb page出post，溫馨提示大家：「收到剛送抵場館之回水杯，經檢查後發現，因製造商在生產回水杯的過程中出現問題，所以由七月二十八日開始及以後出售之回水杯，將會有所瑕疵。介意者請於排隊購買前三思，謝謝各位包涵見諒！」<br />\n<br />\n三更半夜忙完個騷，亦不忘出post（or搵助手出post）溫馨提示大家買真正回水杯要留意嘅地方，試問香港人點可以唔愛你？  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180728/large/1532753986_77f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180728%2Flarge%2F1532753986_77f2.jpg&h=730fe64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨一時，黃子華出post溫馨提示大家佢隻回水杯品質有問題。 （黃子華fb圖片） <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}